#. type: Title ====
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Exception handling"
msgstr "异常处理"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, Quarkus provides a built-in `ExceptionMapper` for `MismatchedInputException` which returns an HTTP 400 status code\n"
"along with a good error message in Dev and Test modes, about what went wrong during serialization of an entity."
msgstr "默认情况下，Quarkus 为 `MismatchedInputException` 提供了一个内置的 `ExceptionMapper` ，该映射器在 Dev 和 Test 模式下会返回 HTTP 400 状态码，并附带一条清晰的错误信息，说明实体序列化过程中出现了什么问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There are situations where various Jackson related exceptions need to handled in a uniform way.For example, the application may need to handle all `JsonMappingException` the same way.\n"
"This becomes a problem when taking JAX-RS / Jakarta REST rules into account, because the exception mapper `ExceptionMapper` for `MismatchedInputException` would be used instead of the user provide\n"
"`ExceptionMapper` for `JsonMappingException` (as `MismatchedInputException` is a subtype of `JsonMappingException`)."
msgstr "在某些情况下，需要以统一的方式处理各种与Jackson相关的异常。例如，应用程序可能需要以相同的方式处理所有 `JsonMappingException异常` 。 但当考虑到 JAX-RS / Jakarta REST 规则时，这便会成为一个问题，因为系统会使用 `MismatchedInputException` 的异常映射器 `ExceptionMapper，` 而不是用户为 `JsonMappingException` 提供的 `ExceptionMapper` （因为 `MismatchedInputException` 是 `JsonMappingException` 的子类型）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To handle this, you can disable the built-in exception mapper:"
msgstr "要解决这个问题，你可以禁用内置的异常映射器："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This allows your custom `ExceptionMapper` for `JsonMappingException` to handle all its subclasses, including `MismatchedInputException`."
msgstr "这样，您为 `JsonMappingException` 创建的自定义 `ExceptionMapper` 就能处理其所有子类，包括 `MismatchedInputException` 。"

#. type: Title ====
