#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In Quarkus, the Quarkus REST extension and xref:rest-client.adoc[the REST Client extension] share the same infrastructure.\n"
